This device is assumed to be using QCA9558 for the (Wi [2.4GHz])SoC. :The '''QCA''' chip is using '''Microchip''' ('''SST''') PAMs. It likely uses AR9380 / AR9580 for the modular 5GHz radio. :The modular radio looks to be using three [http://www.skyworksinc.com/Product.aspx?ProductID=969 '''Skyworks''' ('''SiGe''') SE5003L / 5003L PAMs].
The default SSIDs formats are '''dlink-XXXX''' and '''dlink-XXXX-media'''.
